rge.png?m=1738805593", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/df8b/092d/197545_xlarge.png?m=1738805593", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/df8b/092d/197545_xlarge.png?m=1738805593", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/df8b/092d/197545_xlarge.png?m=1738805593", "created": 1477042003, "last_modified": 1738805593}, "last_reply_by": "zapper", "last_touched": 1748822680, "title": "为什么没有左脚刹车右脚油门的设计呢？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1135739", "created": 1748777155, "deleted": 0, "content": "如题，自动变速器干掉了左脚离合器踏板后，激进的技术流(如特斯拉)想直接进化到单脚油门复合刹车的设计\r\n结果各种事故撞的满头包，多数厂商还是坚持传统的右脚刹车+油门的设计\r\n\r\n为什么没有左脚刹车右脚油门的设计呢？\r\n\r\n或者左脚刹车，右脚油门复合刹车(动力回收)的设计过渡一段，培养消费者习惯，逐渐把左脚刹车改成选配，逐渐取消掉", "content_rendered": "<p>如题，自动变速器干掉了左脚离合器踏板后，激进的技术流(如特斯拉)想直接进化到单脚油门复合刹车的设计\n结果各种事故撞的满头包，多数厂商还是坚持传统的右脚刹车+油门的设计</p>\n<p>为什么没有左脚刹车右脚油门的设计呢？</p>\n<p>或者左脚刹车，右脚油门复合刹车(动力回收)的设计过渡一段，培养消费者习惯，逐渐把左脚刹车改成选配，逐渐取消掉</p>\n", "last_modified": 1748777155, "replies": 27, "id": 1135739}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/7f39/f831/61_large.png?m=1659331290", "name": "mysql", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/7f39/f831/61_normal.png?m=1659331290", "title": "MySQL", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/mysql", "topics": 2008, "footer": "", "header": "地球上最流行的关系数据库。被大量的互联网企业运用在网站项目中。具有非常丰富的生态系统。", "title_alternative": "MySQL", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/7f39/f831/61_mini.png?m=1659331290", "stars": 2225, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 61, "parent_node_name": "db"}, "member": {"id": 635411, "username": "ZimaBlueee", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/ZimaBlueee", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4bd6/c5ae/635411_mini.png?m=1741657885", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4bd6/c5ae/635411_normal.png?m=1741657885", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4bd6/c5ae/635411_large.png?m=1741657885", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4bd6/c5ae/635411_xlarge.png?m=1741657885", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4bd6/c5ae/635411_xlarge.png?m=1741657885", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4bd6/c5ae/635411_xlarge.png?m=1741657885", "created": 1687445278, "last_modified": 1741657885}, "last_reply_by": "Flourite", "last_touched": 1748838621, "title": "《高性能 MySQL》第三版：是否已经过时？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1135741", "created": 1748779081, "deleted": 0, "content": "5 年 Java 后端开发，一直没深入学习过 MySQL ，平时只是使用，不了解 MySQL 原理或者性能优化。\r\n\r\n搜了下看到很多人推荐《高性能 MySQL 》这本书，但发现几个问题：\r\n\r\n- 这本书的第三版评价很高，但是基于**5.5**写的；\r\n- 第四版增加了大量对 MySQL**5.7**和**8.0**版本新特性的介绍，但是豆瓣上的评价说翻译的不好。\r\n\r\n请问有读过的 V 友推荐一下现在学习 MySQL 该读哪本书籍，或者哪个老师的视频呢？\r\n\r\n跪求解答！", "content_rendered": "<p>5 年 Java 后端开发，一直没深入学习过 MySQL ，平时只是使用，不了解 MySQL 原理或者性能优化。</p>\n<p>搜了下看到很多人推荐《高性能 MySQL 》这本书，但发现几个问题：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>这本书的第三版评价很高，但是基于<strong>5.5</strong>写的；</li>\n<li>第四版增加了大量对 MySQL<strong>5.7</strong>和<strong>8.0</strong>版本新特性的介绍，但是豆瓣上的评价说翻译的不好。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>请问有读过的 V 友推荐一下现在学习 MySQL 该读哪本书籍，或者哪个老师的视频呢？</p>\n<p>跪求解答！</p>\n", "last_modified": 1748779081, "replies": 23, "id": 1135741}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1747623425", "name": "life", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1747623425", "title": "生活", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/life", "topics": 8038, "footer": "", "header": "生活中的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Life", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1747623425", "stars": 1850, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 557, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 745276, "username": "zhang666", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/zhang666", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/1454fdbcf38cee9036b2616e868134d0?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/1454fdbcf38cee9036b2616e868134d0?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/1454fdbcf38cee9036b2616e868134d0?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1745379275, "last_modified": 1745475382}, "last_reply_by": "NewYear", "last_touched": 1748840166, "title": "买刮刮乐，中了 20，接下来你会怎么选？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1135800", "created": 1748834314, "deleted": 0, "content": "A：拿 20 领了，不继续买。\nB：再刮一张。\n\n\n本人选了 B ，当时考虑过 A 综合之后还是 B 。再买了一张后，什么也没中，后 B 选 A ，这就是赌徒心态。人总在权衡取舍，选择后又后悔没选择哪个，如果选了，会更好…", "content_rendered": "A：拿 20 领了，不继续买。<br />B：再刮一张。<br /><br /><br />本人选了 B ，当时考虑过 A 综合之后还是 B 。再买了一张后，什么也没中，后 B 选 A ，这就是赌徒心态。人总在权衡取舍，选择后又后悔没选择哪个，如果选了，会更好…", "last_modified": 1748834457, "replies": 20, "id": 1135800}]